.v2ex.com/gravatar/7a8a658026108da60949fc22378f0d7c?s=24&d=retro", "bio": null, "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/ivanMeng", "tagline": null, "twitter": null, "created": 1607507676, "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/7a8a658026108da60949fc22378f0d7c?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/7a8a658026108da60949fc22378f0d7c?s=24&d=retro", "location": null, "btc": null, "id": 523097}, "last_reply_by": "azurefang", "last_touched": 1610074101, "title": "非技术话题。疣怎么彻底去除？大家有经验吗？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/742496", "created": 1609991610, "content": "左脚小拇指边上长了两个很小挨着的疣，去医院诊断为寻常疣，诊断方案就是采用液氮冷冻，现在已经冷冻过两次了，还是有两个小白泡 看来还是没冻死，贴吧众说纷纭 广告一堆也都是乱推荐涂抹药物 用什么各种偏方泡脚 去药房买什么药物自配涂抹等等，不是觉得不可取 因为自己没实践也不确定是否管用，反正医院的方案就是 冷冻 激光 ，没任何药物配合，这玩意还会自身接种感染，自己还不能瞎搞，有没有老铁分享一下怎么去掉这玩意的。感谢。", "content_rendered": "<p>左脚小拇指边上长了两个很小挨着的疣，去医院诊断为寻常疣，诊断方案就是采用液氮冷冻，现在已经冷冻过两次了，还是有两个小白泡 看来还是没冻死，贴吧众说纷纭 广告一堆也都是乱推荐涂抹药物 用什么各种偏方泡脚 去药房买什么药物自配涂抹等等，不是觉得不可取 因为自己没实践也不确定是否管用，反正医院的方案就是 冷冻 激光 ，没任何药物配合，这玩意还会自身接种感染，自己还不能瞎搞，有没有老铁分享一下怎么去掉这玩意的。感谢。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1609998189, "replies": 93, "id": 742496}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6512/bd43/11_large.png?m=1604596625", "name": "linux", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6512/bd43/11_normal.png?m=1604596625", "title": "Linux", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/linux", "topics": 5950, "footer": "", "header": "Linux is a Unix-like computer operating system assembled under the model of free and open source software development and distribution.", "title_alternative": "Linux", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6512/bd43/11_mini.png?m=1604596625", "stars": 5390, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 11, "parent_node_name": "os"}, "member": {"username": "hantsy", "website": "http://hantsy.blogspot.com", "github": "hantsy", "psn": "", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/cbb75897ee67011990d4706fad19e38b?s=24&d=retro", "bio": "", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/hantsy", "tagline": "Coding for Food", "twitter": "", "created": 1440127826, "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/cbb75897ee67011990d4706fad19e38b?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/cbb75897ee67011990d4706fad19e38b?s=24&d=retro", "location": "ShangHai", "btc": "", "id": 134152}, "last_reply_by": "hantsy", "last_touched": 1610074395, "title": "红旗 Linux 居然炸尸了", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/742526", "created": 1609998379, "content": "https://www.oschina.net/news/125744/redflag-linux-11-will-release\r\n\r\n\r\n印象中仅安装一次 RedFlag，满满 Redhat 味道。当时图标，UI 很山寨，用过一次就不再用了。\r\n\r\n最多的时候，RedFlag 的开发人员是到了 100-200 人的规模，大众对其产品几乎没什么印象。\r\n\r\n这次在 Debian 基础上又是重新换图，标界面的操作，又遇到“去这去那”的国产潮，不知道这次能玩多久。", "content_rendered": "<p><a href=\"https://www.oschina.net/news/125744/redflag-linux-11-will-release\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://www.oschina.net/news/125744/redflag-linux-11-will-release</a></p>\n<p>印象中仅安装一次 RedFlag，满满 Redhat 味道。当时图标，UI 很山寨，用过一次就不再用了。</p>\n<p>最多的时候，RedFlag 的开发人员是到了 100-200 人的规模，大众对其产品几乎没什么印象。</p>\n<p>这次在 Debian 基础上又是重新换图，标界面的操作，又遇到“去这去那”的国产潮，不知道这次能玩多久。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1609998379, "replies": 75, "id": 742526}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_large.png?m=1608686051", "name": "apple", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_normal.png?m=1608686051", "title": "Apple", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/apple", "topics": 13601, "footer": "", "header": "设计了 <a href=\"/go/watch\">Apple Watch</a>，<a href=\"/go/ipad\">iPad</a>，<a href=\"/go/iphone\">iPhone</a>，<a href=\"/go/imac\">iMac</a> 及 <a href=\"/go/mbp\">MacBook Pro</a> 等电子产品的美国公司。", "title_alternative": "Apple", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_mini.png?m=1608686051", "stars": 1664, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 184, "parent_node_name": "hardware"}, "member": {"username": "Licardo", "website": "https://licardo.cn", "github": "l1cardo", "psn": "", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e565/b5ce/459578_mini.png?m=1610006740", "bio":